highlights.text: “เจ้าของที่ (My Favorite)” by Mirrr has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 1239 days straight.
YOUNGOHM has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “นครดารา” is the highest at #4.
“ไกล” by Musketeers is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 44 spots at #93.
